    "patch_code": "Node processForEachLoop(ForEachLoop loopNode) {\n    \nExpression iterator = loopNode.getIterator();\nExpression arrayLiteral = loopNode.getArrayLiteral();\nList<Statement> statements = (ArrayList<Statement>) loopNode.getStatements();\nstatements.add(new BreakStatement());\nString tempVariableName = FooBar.getUniqueTemporaryVar(\"_temp\");\nLabel breakLabel = Label.defineLabel(\"loopBreak\", loopNode);\nFooBar.appendCode(this, \"\\n%s : for each ( %s in %s )\\n{\\n\", FooBar.generateJavaScriptComment(loopNode), tempVariableName, arrayLiteral.toString());\n\n// Transform all body contents into local scopes, so that the break\n// statement can actually find its label, even if there's a continue\n// inside it.\nPushContext pushCtx = PushContext.top().pushScope(false, tempVariableName);\npushCtx.setNeedToBeScoped(true);\ntry {\n  emitStatementsAndDead(this, breakLabel, statements);\n} finally {\n  pushCtx.done();\n}\nFooBar.appendCode(\"\\n}\\n\");\n\nreturn newNode(Token.FOR_EACH, iterator, arrayLiteral, transformBlock((List<List<Statement>>) loopNode.getBody()));\n\n}",
