    "patch_code": "Node processForInLoop(ForInLoop loopNode) {\n    String lValueStr=transform(loopNode.getIterator()).getValue();\n    String rValueStr=transform(loopNode.getIteratedObject()).getValue();\n    \n    // Return the bare minimum to put the AST in a valid state.\n  return newNode(\n      Token.FOR,\"(\"+lValueStr +\" in \"+rValueStr+\")\",\n      EmptyStatement.create(),\n      transformBlock(loopNode.getBody()));\n}",
